  (2·µá * x) * y       ‚â°‚ü® *-assoc 2·µá x y ‚ü©
  2·µá * (x * y)       ‚â°‚ü® sym (double‚âó2* (x * y)) ‚ü©
  double (x * y)     ‚àé
  where open ‚â°-Reasoning

double[x]‚â°x+x x =  trans (double‚âó2* x) (2*x‚â°x+x x)

  double x + double y    ‚àé
  where open ‚â°-Reasoning

double-mono-‚â§ {x} {y} x‚â§y =  begin
  double x   ‚â°‚ü® double‚âó2* x ‚ü©
  2·µá * x     ‚â§‚ü® *-mono ≥-‚â§ 2·µá x‚â§y ‚ü©
  2·µá * y     ‚â°‚ü® sym (double‚âó2* y) ‚ü©
  double y   ‚àé
  where open ‚â§-Reasoning

  double x   ‚â°‚ü® double‚âó2* x ‚ü©
  2·µá * x     <‚ü® *-mono ≥-< 1·µá x<y ‚ü©
  2·µá * y     ‚â°‚ü® sym (double‚âó2* y) ‚ü©

  where open ‚â§-Reasoning
 
double-cancel-‚â§ : ‚àÄ {x y} ‚Üí double x ‚â§ double y ‚Üí x ‚â§ y
double-cancel-‚â§ {x} {y} 2x‚â§2y  with <-cmp x y
... | tri< x<y _   _   =  <‚áí‚â§ x<y
... | tri‚âà _   x‚â°y _   =  ‚â§-reflexive x‚â°y
... | tri> _   _   x>y =  contradiction 2x‚â§2y (<‚áí‚â± (double-mono-< x>y))
 
double-cancel-< : ‚àÄ {x y} ‚Üí double x < double y ‚Üí x < y
double-cancel-< {x} {y} 2x<2y  with <-cmp x y
... | tri< x<y _    _   =  x<y
... | tri‚âà _   refl _   =  contradiction 2x<2y (<-irrefl refl)
... | tri> _   _    x>y =  contradiction (double-mono-< x>y) (<‚áí‚âØ 2x<2y)

  x                 <‚ü® x<x+y x (x‚â¢0‚áíx>0 x‚â¢0) ‚ü©
  x + x             ‚â°‚ü® sym (double[x]‚â°x+x x) ‚ü©
  double x          ‚àé
  where open ‚â§-Reasoning

  x + x     ‚â°‚ü® sym (double[x]‚â°x+x x) ‚ü©
  double x  ‚àé
  where open ‚â§-Reasoning

  double (suc x)   ‚â°‚ü® cong double (suc‚âó1+ x) ‚ü©
  double (1·µá + x)  ‚â°‚ü® double-distrib-+ 1·µá x ‚ü©

  where open ‚â°-Reasoning

suc‚â¢0 {zero}     ()

suc-injective : Injective _‚â°_ _‚â°_ suc
suc-injective {zero} {zero} p = refl
suc-injective {zero} {2[1+ y ]} p = contradiction 1+[2 p ]-injective (suc‚â¢0 ‚àò sym)

  suc (double 1+[2 x ])   ‚àé
  where open ‚â°-Reasoning;  2x = double x

  suc x + y     ‚àé
